@startuml
title Facility Cost Report

|Super Admin or Facility Admin|
start
:Open facility cost report page;
:Enter report criteria;
:Submit request;

|System|

  if (Criteria valid?) then (Yes)

    fork
      :Retrieve facility cost data;
    fork again
      :Retrieve usage/category data;
    end fork

    :Calculate totals and breakdowns;
    :Generate report;

    fork
      :Display report;
    fork again
      :Record report access in log;
    end fork

    if (Export (CSV/PDF) requested?) then (Yes)
      :Generate export file;
      :Provide download;
    else (No)  
    endif

  else (No)
    :Show validation errors;
  endif

end

@enduml